text: Uhnin is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Dębowa Kłoda, within Parczew County, Lublin Voivodeship, in eastern Poland. It lies approximately south-east of Dębowa Kłoda, south-east of Parczew, and north- east of the regional capital Lublin. ==References== Uhnin Category:Kholm Governorate
